         <abstract>
            <p>This paper concerns the $L_2$-projectors from $L_\infty$ to the normed linear space of polynomial splines. It is shown that for the multiple geometric meshes the $L_\infty$ norms of the corresponding $L_2$-projectors are bounded independently of the mesh ratio.</p>
          </abstract>
